# add aosp art
if (${AOSP_ART})
    message("enable aosp art")

    # add aosp art header dir
    include_directories(
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/libdexfile/external/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/libnativebridge/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/libnativeloader/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/openjdkjvmti/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/sigchainlib"
    )

    # add aosp art header file
    file(GLOB_RECURSE HEADERS_ART
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/libdexfile/external/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/libnativebridge/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/libnativeloader/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/openjdkjvmti/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/art/sigchainlib/**/*.h"
            )
    # append aosp art header
    list(APPEND HEADERS ${HEADERS_ART})
endif ()


# add aosp bionic
if (${AOSP_BIONIC})
    message("enable aosp bionic")

    # add aosp bionic header dir
    include_directories(
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/async_safe/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/dns/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/kernel"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/kernel/android/scsi"

            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/kernel/uapi"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/kernel/uapi/asm-arm64"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/malloc_debug"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/platform"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/seccomp/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/system_properties/include"
    )

    # add aosp bionic header file
    file(GLOB_RECURSE HEADERS_BIONIC
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/async_safe/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/dns/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/include/**/*.h"

            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/kernel/uapi/asm-arm64/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/malloc_debug/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/platform/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/seccomp/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/bionic/libc/system_properties/include/**/*.h"
            )
    # append aosp bionic header
    list(APPEND HEADERS ${HEADERS_BIONIC})
endif ()

# add aosp packages
if (${AOSP_PACKAGES})
    message("enable aosp packages")

    # add aosp packages src
    file(GLOB SOURCE_FILES_PACKAGES
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Bluetooth/system/gd/hci/*.cc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Bluetooth/system/gd/packet/*.cc
            )
    # append aosp packages src
    list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${SOURCE_FILES_PACKAGES})

    # add aosp packages header dir
    include_directories(
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Bluetooth/system/gd"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Bluetooth/system/types"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/DnsResolver/include/dnsproxyd_protocol"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Gki/libkver/include"

            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/NeuralNetworks/common/types/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/NeuralNetworks/runtime/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/NeuralNetworks/tools/test_generator/test_harness/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/StatsD/lib/libkll/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/StatsD/lib/libstatspull/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/StatsD/lib/libstatssocket/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Virtualization/microdroid/payload/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/adb/pairing_connection/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/services/Car/cpp/car_binder_lib/largeParcelable/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/services/Car/cpp/powerpolicy/client/include"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/services/Car/cpp/vhal/client/include"
    )

    # add aosp packages header file
    file(GLOB_RECURSE HEADERS_PACKAGES
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Bluetooth/system/gd/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Bluetooth/system/types/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/DnsResolver/include/dnsproxyd_protocol/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/Gki/libkver/include/**/*.h"
            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/NeuralNetworks/common/include/**/*.h"

            "${ANDROID_ROOT}/packages/modules/NeuralNetworks/runtime/include/**/*.h"
